## ğŸ“– Description

Experimental arbitrage bot developed in Rust for the Base blockchain (Ethereum L2). The project aimed to detect and execute arbitrage opportunities on decentralized exchanges (Uniswap V3 and Aerodrome).

### Implemented Strategies

1. **Classic Arbitrage (2-leg)**: Detection of price discrepancies between two DEXs for the same token pair
2. **Triangular Arbitrage (3-leg)**: Exploitation of price inefficiencies across 3-token cycles (e.g., USDC â†’ WETH â†’ DAI â†’ USDC)



